snippet.title: Libre TrainSim: Preview for v0.8 (Under Development)
snippet.description:
Please keep in mind that this version is currently under development, and not available yet.
The release of version Libre TrainSim is in early summer!

Libre TrainSim is an open source project, which creates a complete new, fully free Train Simulator written in Godot Engine, which is released under GPL 3.0.

Get Libre TrainSim for free at: https://www.libre-trainsim.de
